      • isTagged

        boolean isTagged(String repositoryUuid,
                 IBranchPath branchPath)
        Deprecated. 
        Returns true if the given branch has been tagged in the specified repository. Otherwise returns false.

        More formally, this method returns with true only and if only a code system exists for the given repository, and the code system has at least one associated code system version with the same version ID as the last segment of the branch path argument. Otherwise returns with false.

        Parameters:
        repositoryUuid - the repository UUID.
        branchPath - the branch to check if tagged or not.
        Returns:
        true if the branch is tagged, otherwise false.

      • isPatched

        boolean isPatched(String repositoryUuid,
                  IBranchPath branchPath)
        Deprecated. 
        Returns true if the given branch path represents a tag in the repository and modifications have been made on the version tag. Otherwise returns with false.
        Parameters:
        repositoryUuid - the unique ID of the repository.
        branchPath - the unique path of the branch to check.
        Returns:
        true if the branch has been tagged and modifications have been made on it. Otherwise false.

      • getAllTags

        Collection<ICodeSystemVersion> getAllTags(String repositoryUuid)
        Deprecated. 
        Returns with all registered tags (code system versions) available in a repository given with the unique repository identifier.

        A matching code system version is representing a valid tag only and if only the corresponding maintenance branch is available for it.

        Parameters:
        repositoryUuid - the unique repository identifier.
        Returns:
        a collection of code system versions (tags).

      • getAllPatchedTags

        List<ICodeSystemVersion> getAllPatchedTags(String repositoryUuid)
        Deprecated. 
        Returns with a list of patched versions. Clients are guaranteed that all ICodeSystemVersion representing a branch has modifications since it has been created.
        Parameters:
        repositoryUuid - the repository UUID.
        Returns:
        a list of patched tags. Or empty list if no such tags.

      • getAllTagsWithHead

        List<ICodeSystemVersion> getAllTagsWithHead(String repositoryUuid)
        Deprecated. 
        Returns with all tags (code system versions) including the HEAD for the given repository.
        The list of code system versions are sorted via the import date in descending order. HEAD is the first, then the others.

        A matching code system version is representing a valid tag only and if only the corresponding maintenance branch is available for it.

        Parameters:
        repositoryUuid - the unique ID of the repository.
        Returns:
        a list of all available tags including the HEAD.
